&lt;p&gt;We will now run the evaluation suite over the entire &lt;code&gt;gate dataset&lt;/code&gt; for all the models in the above list.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div id="cell-45" class="cell" data-execution_count="427"&gt;
&lt;details class="code-fold"&gt;
